title: John Mulaney | The 2020 Election Is Here -- and Trump Is Trying to Steal It: A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at Trump threatening to prematurely declare victory and steal the election through the courts.

Then, Seth talks to John Mulaney. (Plus, a special digital-only segment in which John asks Seth some personal questions.)
